🏛️ What is the Baldesion Annex?

The Baldesion Annex is a satellite branch of the Students of Baldesion, a scholarly organization originally based on the island of Baldesion in the Northern Empty (which was destroyed by a Calamity).

  • Location: Old Sharlayan (Labyrinthos, on the lower western edge of the map).

  • Function: Serves as a research facility and base of operations for Scions and allied scholars.

  • Affiliation: Tied to the Scions of the Seventh Dawn, especially during the events of Endwalker.

  • Leadership: Krile Mayer Baldesion, one of the Scions and a key character, is the representative and caretaker of the annex.

📚 Lore Context

  • The original Baldesion Institute was destroyed in a mysterious aetheric explosion during the events between A Realm Reborn and Heavensward.

  • The Annex in Old Sharlayan represents the rebuilding effort, a revival of its mission to study magic, aether, and the mysteries of the star.

  • It becomes a hub for many quests and lore-heavy conversations, particularly involving research into dynamis, aetherology, and ancient civilizations.

🧭 In-Game Use

  • Unlocked via Endwalker MSQ.

  • Acts as a hub for several side quests and optional content, including Custom Deliveries for Ameliance Leveilleur.

  • Contains vendors, interactable NPCs, and lore objects.
